					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-413292#post-4105902</guid>
				<title>Coincidence?</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-413292/scp-1018#post-4105902</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 02 Jan 2019 07:25:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MrShekel</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4996934</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&quot;Are we Cool yet?&quot; The same phrase was said by a D-Class personnel while under the influence of SCP-1074. Was this &quot;art installation&quot; created by the same group/entity?</p> 
