					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-413292#post-1478591</guid>
				<title>Finally</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-413292/scp-1018#post-1478591</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 13 Jun 2012 00:50:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Hurtz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1328710</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I was going to head back here after its Cameo in <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/the-critic">The Critic</a> to ask if anyone has noticed the fridge horror that while this doesn't just randomly kill people nearby, they had to get the images of dehydrated emaciated children from somewhere&#8230;</p> <p>To see that someone else had finally broached the topic.</p> <p>In my head canon, yes. Yes they did.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-413292#post-1472930</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
